# URL Shortener - Django Project

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.8+-blue)
![Django](https://img.shields.io/badge/Django-3.x/4.x-green)
![Bootstrap](https://img.shields.io/badge/Bootstrap-5-purple)

**GitHub Repo:** [https://github.com/vishnuvm1122/url-shortner](https://github.com/vishnuvm1122/url-shortner)

---

## ðŸ“„ Description
A Django-based **URL Shortener** application that allows users to:
- Create **short URLs** for long URLs
- Track the number of clicks per URL
- Manage URLs in a **user dashboard**
- Redirect short URLs to the original URLs
- View click details including **IP, browser, platform, and device**

---

## ðŸ‘¤ User Authentication & Profile Features
- **User Registration** with username, email, and password
- **Login** and Logout functionality
- **Profile Update** (username, email, first name, last name)
- **Password Change** with old password verification
- Form validation with helpful error messages
- Bootstrap 5 styling for all forms
- Flash messages for user feedback

---

## ðŸ”— URL Shortening Features
- Create **short URLs** with unique 6-character or 10-character UIDs
- **Edit** or **delete** your own URLs
- Auto-increment click count per URL
- Redirect short URL to the original URL safely
- **AJAX support** for dynamic URL creation, editing, and deletion

---

## ðŸ“Š Click Tracking Features
- Records **IP address, browser, platform, and device** for each click
- Click details displayed per URL for logged-in users
- Ability to **delete individual click records**
- Admin panel support for viewing click history

---

## ðŸ›  Admin Panel Features
- Full management of `Url` and `UrlClick` models
- **Search** and **filter** URLs and clicks
- Click counts and URL preview directly in admin
- Short URL links clickable in admin for quick access

---

